{"title":"悼念阎红彦同志","authors":["魏传统"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼念阎红彦同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏传统"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原云南省委第一书记阎红彦同志，于一九六七年一月八日，在昆明被迫害致死。至今已有十五年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆昔延安同学日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秉性不阿诚刚直。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年华正茂无所惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛斥歪风堪及时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北驰驱度一生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东西熬过无数春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"料君九泉未忘我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃熄自身慰英灵。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}